research_municipality_step.notes: The City of San Benito, TX operates under a mayor-commission form of government. The names and roles of the elected officials were primarily sourced from the City of San Benito's official website and the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory. Some minor variations in the spelling of names (e.g., 'Thomas W. Goodman II' vs. 'Tom W. Goodman, II' or 'Pedro A. Galvan, Pharm D.' vs. 'Pete A. Galvan, Pharm. D.') were noted across different sources; the most complete versions were used.
